.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-LOCAL-COUNT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-local-count \- FEAT-2706 node-listforwards-local-count
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-local-count
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the count of local-origin forwards for this node (FEAT-2706).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN containing \fBlocal_forward_count\fR (int).
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
